Introduction

This article offers a series of tips I have picked up throughout the course of my career fixing performance problems for big enterprises. I will describe systematic ways to find and fix the three most impactful issues in my experience using a tool I have created called javOSize.



“Top 10 Java Performance Problems” sets out three of the most common and harmful pitfalls you’ll experience with the platform:

Thread deadlocks

Memory leaks
